::Skulletron::

	Skulletron pulled out a Maximal symbol that would look perfect on his
chest.  He placed it on, and then saw that Feline had a symbol on her
shoulder, and holding another symbol, and she asked if he wanted it.

	"Uh, no thanks, I got one already," Skulletron said, shivering.
